OL,3,CBrimscombe community grieves for
OL,4,Cmother and children killed in Boxing
OL,5,CDay fire
OL,7,FThe community of Brimscombe has paid
OL,8,Ftribute to a mother and her two
OL,9,Fchildren who died on Boxing Day.
OL,11,FFionnghuala Shearman, known as Nu,
OL,12,Fseven-year-old Eve and four-year-old
OL,13,FOhner died in a fire at their home on
OL,14,F26 December 2025.
OL,16,FFlowers and messages of condolence
OL,17,Fwere initially placed at the property
OL,18,Fon Brimscombe Hill but were moved at
OL,19,Fthe family's request to Holy Trinity
OL,20,FChurch in Minchinhampton.
