OL,3,CBrimscombe community grieves for
OL,4,Cmother and children killed in Boxing
OL,5,CDay fire
OL,7,FNu, Eve and Ohner had visited the
OL,8,Fchurch for a Christmas Eve service two
OL,9,Fdays before their death.
OL,11,FThey are survived by husband and
OL,12,Ffather Tom Shearman, an officer with
OL,13,FGloucestershire Police who tried to
OL,14,Frescue his family from the fire at the
OL,15,Fproperty on Brimscombe Hill.
OL,17,FOfficers from neighbouring Avon and
OL,18,FSomerset Police have been brought in
OL,19,Fto protect the home as Gloucestershire
OL,20,FPolice officers mourn their
OL,21,Fcolleague's loss.
