OL,7,F"They were a family who were very well
OL,8,Floved and liked, so the response has
OL,9,Fbeen huge," said Reverend Tracey
OL,10,FClements.
OL,12,F"I've been in contact with the family
OL,13,Fto assure them that we're here, and
OL,14,Fspoken to Tom's mum, and I understand
OL,15,Fhe's being very, very well looked-
OL,16,Fafter by his colleagues at work and
OL,17,Fthe family. But obviously it's
OL,18,Fdevastating for all of them."
