OL,3,CBrimscombe community grieves for
OL,4,Cmother and children killed in Boxing
OL,5,CDay fire
OL,7,FBrimscombe Mill, a community hub in
OL,8,Fthe town, was closed for Christmas but
OL,9,Fhas opened to allow well-wishers to
OL,10,Fleave flowers and write in a book of
OL,11,Fcondolence for the family.
OL,13,FEd Sauven from Brimscombe Mill said
OL,14,Fthe family were well known in the area.
OL,16,F"The more (you) chat to people, the
OL,17,Fmore connections you realise. They
OL,18,Fwere - they are - a beautiful family,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
