OL,3,CBrimscombe community grieves for
OL,4,Cmother and children killed in Boxing
OL,5,CDay fire
OL,7,FOn 2 January 2026, local football team
OL,8,FBrimscombe and Thrupp FC dedicated
OL,9,Ftheir match against Stonehouse Town FC
OL,10,Fto Tom and his family.
OL,12,FThey held a minute's silence and asked
OL,13,Ffor donations to support the family.
OL,15,FThe money will add to the #400,000
OL,16,Falready raised by a GoFundMe page set
OL,17,Fup on Sunday 28 December to support
OL,18,FTom.
